Upload Protocol (Section 12.6 binding)
•Upload initiates an upload_session_id
•Chunked transport: each chunk confirmed before next is sent
•upload_status transitions: pending → in_progress → staged → complete
•upload_status = "complete" only after full chunk manifest confirmed AND staging durability confirmed
•"Complete" shown to user only after complete status set AND evidence_upload_completed event emitted
•No silent drop on failure: upload_status = "failed" + evidence_upload_failed event emitted
•Resume: upload_session_id allows resuming from last confirmed chunk

