3.2.10 — Object 9: ScanJob
🆕 NEW OBJECT REQUIRED  Section 10.2 defines Quick Scan and Deep Scan entitlement logic in detail. No `scan_jobs` table exists. This is a critical MVP object — it governs credit deduction, caching, and rate limiting.

Canonical Name	ScanJob
