Mutation Rules
•Quick Scan: ScanJob created after rate-limit check passes (4 per 7-day window per paid trip; 2 lifetime per free tier)
•Deep Scan: ScanJob creation requires explicit user_confirmed_at timestamp. No auto-execution.
•credit_consumed: set to true atomically with deep_scan_credit_consumed ledger event. Never set before that event.
•cached_hit: if itinerary_hash + account_id matches an existing completed ScanJob in rolling window, return that result; do not create new ScanJob; do not consume credit

