This amendment formally resolves all 10 open narrative clarification questions from Section 3.2.32 (v1.1). Questions Q1–Q6 originated in v1.0. Questions Q7–Q10 were added in v1.1 to cover voice narration conflicts, readiness gating, activity rejection feedback, and group collaboration.
 
